 \n| \n| 1990 \n|- \n| Island of Desire \n| Father of Molly\n| 1990 (Date of Released: October 6, 1990)\n|- \n| Shake, Rattle & Roll 2\n| Dr. Corpus (segment \"Multo\") \n| 1990 \n|- \n| Una Kang Naging Akin \n| Dr. Mallari \n| 1991 (Date of Released: September 25, 1991)\n|- \n| Itakwil Man Ako ng Langit \n| \n| 1991 \n|- \n| Uubusin Ko Ang Lahi Mo \n| \n| 1991 \n|- \n| Magdaleno Orbos: Sa Kuko ng Mga Lawin\n| Mr. Alingcastre \n| 1991 (Date of Released: November 13, 1991)\n|- \n| Humanap Ka ng Panget \n| Ernesto \n| 1991 \n|- \n| Kailan Ka Magiging Akin \n| Jaime \n| 1991 \n|- \n| Andrew Ford Medina: Wag Kang Gamol!\n| Ernesto \n| 1991 \n|- \n| Kumukulong Dugo\n| Moreno \n| 1991 (Date of Released: October 23, 1991)\n|- \n| Buburahin Kita Sa Mundo!\n|\n| 1991\n|-\n| Ikaw Pa Lang Ang Minahal\n| Maximo \n| 1992 \n|- \n| Pat. Omar Abdullah: Pulis Probinsiya \n| Cong. Angelo Ampil\n| 1992 (Date of Released: September 9, 1992)\n|- \n| Iisa Pa Lamang \n| Ramon \n| 1992 (Date of Released: May 6, 1992)\n|- \n| Daddy Goon \n| \n| 1992 \n|- \n| Angelina: The Movie \n| \n| 1992 \n|- \n| Cornelia Ramos Story \n| \n| 1992 \n|- \n| Andres Manambit: Angkan ng Matatapang \n| Mayor Rafael De Jesus\n| 1992 (Date of Released: December 25, 1992 [[Metro Manila Film Festival|MMFF]])\n|- \n| Kailangan Kita\n| Conrad \n| 1993 (Date of Released: March 17, 1993)\n|- \n| Home Along da Riles (The Movie)\n| Governor Quiogue \n| 1993 \n|- \n| Doring Borobo \n| Servanda\n| 1993 (Date of Released: December 25, 1993 [[Metro Manila Film Festival|MMFF]])\n|- \n| Secret Love\n| Ronald \n| 1993 (Date of Released: August 11, 1993)\n|- \n| Sana Ay Ikaw Na Nga \n| \n| 1993 \n|- \n| Makuha Ka Sa Tingin\n| Don Ricardo \n| 1993 \n|- \n| The Untold Story: Vizconde Massacre II \u2013 May The Lord Be With Us \n| \n| 1994 \n|- \n| Ismael Zacarias\n| Don Pablo \n| 1994 (Date of Released: July 27, 1994)\n|- \n| Di Mapigil Ang Init \n| \n| 1995  \n|-\n| Leon Cordero : Duwag Lang Ang Hahalik Sa Lupa!\n| Don Salazar\n